程序包 com.ae2dms.model.gameObject.sprite.character

类 Enemy

java.lang.Object
com.ae2dms.model.gameObject.GameObject
com.ae2dms.model.gameObject.sprite.SpriteObject
com.ae2dms.model.gameObject.sprite.character.Enemy
public class Enemy extends SpriteObject
An Enemy is a non-controllable com.ae2dms.model.gameObject.sprite.character that kills the main.Hero whenever it or its projectile comes in contact. Enemies are able to be bubbled and free themselves from these bubbles after a period of time. Enemies change direction at random intervals, when hitting a wall, and when hitting the main.Hero's shield. Enemies jump at random intervals as well.
